rs and families seeking mid-range properties. This trend is also reflected in a dip in Kochi's House Price Index, with businesses favoring well-connected highway regions.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/highway-expansion-redraws-kochis-real-estate-map/129388906?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-236204/129388906.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}]}